## Syntax highlighting for Hoverfly

syntax hoverfly "\.hf$"
comment "::"

#arrows
color brightcyan "(<=|=>)"

#imports
color italic,lightblue "^[ ]*<= .*$"

#variables
color bold,lagoon "(#|\^|&)[ \t]*[0-9]+"

#strings
color cyan ""([^"\]|\\.)*"|""""

#trailing whitespace
color ,green "[ ]+$"

#comments
color grey "^[ ]*::.*$"
